    <stitle>HOOD, GRILLE, FENDERS AND BUMPER - 7000 - 7000 Model Series - GRILLE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="2">
        <title>GRILLE</title>
        <para>The grille on the 7000 series is available in two (2) styles. The first is a two-piece fiberglass grille
            and shroud bolted to the hood, and is furnished in a chrome finish. This grille on the 7000 series model can
            be removed without removing the hood. The second option is a fixed grille which is secured to the radiator
            frame assembly and remains stationary when the hood is tilted. The grille shroud is attached to the hood
            assembly and tilts with the hood.
        </para>
